metadata.title: Western Arctic CTD Data (1986-1989)

creators.name: Atmospheric Research (OAR), Pacific Marine Environmental Laboratory (PMEL)

metadata.description: CTD data were collected over the Bering and Chukchi Sea from 1986 to 1989, using SeaBird CTD's during the Freeze, CSCS and OCSEAP projects. NOAAServer Codes:   [L 74 62 -140 -175] ; nodateline.
